tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE eeg_analysis_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    subject_id INT,
    condition_id INT,
    analysis_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    analysis_result JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE patient_info (
    patient_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name TEXT,
    age INT,
    gender TEXT,
    condition TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE training_data (
    data_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    eeg_data_id INT,
    network_id INT,
    accuracy FLOAT
);
